lenders.name: Michael
lenders.loan_because: I chose Sweet Petit Desserts because I wanted to support an African American owned small business located in Cincinnati, Ohio.  I am a native Cincinnatian who now lives in Georgia, but know that there is a great deal of opportunity in Cincinnati.  Gaps in lending need to be fill in non-traditional ways so that deserving women entrprenuers can realize their dreams and create diverse business in Cincinnati.

lenders.name: Thomas
lenders.loan_because: Erika is a personal friend of ours, and we know her as a hard working, honest and kind person that shares our values.  We are excited about this venture, and wish her the best of luck.

lenders.name: Mark
lenders.loan_because: I'm a recovering technology entrepreneur who now advises and invests in startups, particularly those that serve a purpose beyond making a profit.  I'm interested in supporting businesses that make the world a better place and improve people's lives.

lenders.name: Bertie
lenders.loan_because: I have a soft spot for ambitious entrepreneurs who have a commitment to paying it forward.
